# EasyPyManager - Python Tool Manager

EasyPyManager is a GUI application for managing and executing Python scripts, supporting both `.py` and `.pyc` files. It automatically extracts script metadata and provides features like grouping, searching, and dependency installation.

## Key Features

Import and manage Python scripts (.py/.pyc)
Automatic metadata extraction or manual input (name, version, description)
Group management for scripts
Real-time search functionality
Customizable Python and pip commands
One-click dependency installation
WHL file installation support
Drag-and-drop file import
Run scripts via double-click or right-click menu

## Installation

1. Ensure Python 3.6+ and PyQt5 are installed
2. Clone or download this project
3. Install:
   pip install easypymanager
